summary: So I know it's described as being like a chest plate, but all I can think of when they talk about Caduceus' armor is like beetle...
body:
So I know it’s described as being like a chest plate, but all I can think of when they talk about Caduceus’ armor is like beetle wing garments. …just this chest plate made of tiny little beetle wing scale mail.

Even if he didn’t have bright pink hair, they’d be able to see him coming a mile off from the iridescence of all the little beetle wings in his armor.
